	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="20153" data-title="《好奇心年度设计大赏之二：过去一年，设计师都认为哪些设计了不起？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/20153/medium/20153.jpg?1451829954" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/20153.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
